    The Book class represents a book entity in the library management system.
    BookDAO
    The BookDAO class is responsible for interacting with the database to perform CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations for Book objects.
    BookDAOInterface
    The BookDAOInterface defines the contract for the data access operations related to Book objects.
    BookForm
    The BookForm class is a parents class for AddBookManually and EditBookDetails.

    The Collection class represents a collection of books associated with a specific user in the library management system.

    The CollectionDAO class provides data access methods for managing Collection records in the database.
    CollectionDAOInterface
    The CollectionDAOInterface defines the contract for data access operations related to Collection objects.
    DatabaseConnector
    The DatabaseConnector class manages the connection to the SQLite database.
    Loan
    The Loan class represents a loan record in the system.
    LoanDAO
    The LoanDAO class provides data access methods for interacting with the Loans table in the database.
    LoanDAOInterface
    The LoanDAOInterface defines the contract for data access operations related to Loan objects.
    LoanService
    The LoanService class provides services for managing loans, including loading, refreshing, adding, and removing loans.

    The LoanServiceInterface defines the contract for mock LoanService functionality.
